nhc_headline: ...OCTAVE HAS CHANGED LITTLE IN ORGANIZATION SINCE EARLIER TODAY...
summary: ...OCTAVE HAS CHANGED LITTLE IN ORGANIZATION SINCE EARLIER TODAY... As of 2:00 PM PDT Thu Oct 02 the center of Octave was located near 12.7, -119.0 with movement WNW at 8 mph. The minimum central pressure was 997 mb with maximum sustained winds of about 60 mph.
